public class Album
extends Model

OpenSocial model class representing an album, a collection of media items. For reference: http://wiki.opensocial.org/index.php?title=Opensocial.Album_(v0.9) http://www.opensocial.org/Technical-Resources/opensocial-spec-v09/REST-API.html#rfc.section.3.6.1
